# TODO -> v2.0 Release

## Scheme
* remove `history-goto-entry`, `history-current-entry-time`, `history-current-entry-line`, and `history-entry-time`.
* expose `current_history()`, `next_history()`, and `previous_history()` API
* refactor `history-position` to use `set_history_pos` directly.
* remove support for offsets relative to the current position.

## C
* add support for highlighting the current paren or brace under the cursor.
